20:45.879 --> 20:48.549
And... it was...

20:48.582 --> 20:52.252
...the most wonderful
day of my life.

20:54.087 --> 20:56.723
And... you...

20:58.324 --> 21:00.661
...made that day possible.

21:05.398 --> 21:07.634
I am so blessed

21:07.668 --> 21:09.836
