Yaya...

21:31.725 --> 21:33.660
...you don't
make things easy.

21:36.496 --> 21:39.933
I've been trying to do
what you told me to do.

21:39.966 --> 21:43.504
To go on with my life
as if nothing has happened.

21:44.871 --> 21:47.340
But... you don't understand

21:47.373 --> 21:49.042
how hard it is...

21:50.777 --> 21:54.648
...because you've
never lost you.

