I made this for you.

22:09.663 --> 22:11.598
[music continues]

22:20.406 --> 22:22.108
I hope you like it.

22:26.547 --> 22:28.849
Um...

22:28.882 --> 22:31.785
Cousin Larry said that...

22:31.818 --> 22:34.154
...I have to say goodbye.

22:34.187 --> 22:35.822
And that...

22:35.856 --> 22:38.491
