22:42.062 --> 22:44.965
And I think he was right.

22:47.100 --> 22:49.002
I miss you.

22:50.871 --> 22:52.606
[sighing]

22:55.475 --> 22:57.978
Well...

22:58.011 --> 23:01.047
...I'm gonna go
upstairs now and...

23:01.081 --> 23:03.684
...tell my friends
that I'm sad.

23:06.219 --> 23:08.622
I think that'll
make them happy.

23:17.230 --> 23:19.800
Bye‐bye, yaya.

23:19.833 --> 23:22.468
